  stimulus_type = NULL,
  options = '[{"id":"A","text":"and it was only active at night, and it had a unique, very complex mating ritual.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice A is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"B","text":"being only active at night and having a unique, very complex mating ritual.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice B is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"C","text":"only active at night, and it had a unique, very complex mating ritual.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"The correct answer is C. The original sentence uses two unnecessary commas.  The phrase \"only active at night\" is a nonessential element that describes the butterfly and can therefore be set off with commas.  \"And it had a unique, very complex mating ritual\" is an independent clause, which cannot be. Choice C matches the question''s requirement and is consistent with the passage''s central claim or supporting detail. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"D","text":"active only at night, and it had a unique, very complex mating ritual.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice D is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."}]'::jsonb,
